{"tid":269371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母上左神檯","createTime":"2017-06-03T16:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T17:23:09.000Z","uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c193898ac5cabe8bdbd4b3afcba346a6694b228","tid":269371,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"本身我老母都幾賢良淑德 <br />\n細細個就覺得大個一定要咁樣<br />\n呢幾年有左v7同同學聚會之後<br />\n老母成日返支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然佢都仲有幾番姿色同少少嘅包裝技巧<br />\n久而久之 我老母俾班同學追棒話佢乜柒班花呀 聚會有佢先人齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家佢勁自我中心 俾人棒到上神檯<br />\n搞到屋企永無寧日<br />\n老豆已經兩次衝動想鋸左我老母<br />\n求各位巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法鋤佢銳氣"},{"pid":"ac592c7e1d65048f1a6565f47ccb7d8c9873ec77","tid":269371,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"鋸左你老母? 不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb5157d2ddec72e7452658c95d0b180a6283d62","tid":269371,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"驚已報"},{"pid":"b808ff2d44033d9f250a35d7bf0d77f54dd2e51c","tid":269371,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鋸左你老母? 不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心入面想啫 安答冷靜"},{"pid":"f754e72d6a4f60f8f522c82c31d3bb6f65ddd2ea","tid":269371,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<br />\n更係啦 跟你老豆咁多做黃面婆<br />\n日日比人點 比人屌<br />\n有番啲成功感 歸屬感更係威啦"},{"pid":"e4218fc1322fbe475eb54bd4df9cb8badf6a98c0","tid":269371,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd4b4a0bbfda983579d6cdb080c7c252f01c3559","tid":269371,"uid":1024